{"tid":1393342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家知唔知私人企業已經開始睇死我地","createTime":"2019-08-01T05:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T09:13:48.000Z","uid":30412,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ddfc1f8c60280c58934c096ed0e711b860da9bf","tid":1393342,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"細佬係私企返工 要跑數 前日腦細開會話依排因爲啲後生仔搞到生意差左好多 <span style=\"color: green;\">不過唔洗驚！照計班𡃁仔好快頂唔順 人愈黎愈少 好似14年咁 佢地玩埋個八月生意就回復正常</span><br />\n<br />\n我屌啊！睇死我地？邊個同你講得後生出黎？<br />\n<br />\n我唔想比班社會垃圾睇死啊 大家頂住啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7x1uME4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7x1uME4.png&h=f8f0ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFf3Q6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFf3Q6L.png&h=f586210d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMaZ8Tr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMaZ8Tr.png&h=2ac7ca53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc0172a078279f9d9004034294c136f1ebe5b535","tid":1393342,"uid":35737,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"𤧶？ 玩佢老母呀 <br />\n下一代用自己嘅未來<br />\n嚟同佢爭取香港人嘅自由 條友可以咁撚自私講啲咁嘅野"},{"pid":"263fe0160421e9588fa83ef7852746124a15f387","tid":1393342,"uid":30412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc0172a078279f9d9004034294c136f1ebe5b535","tid":1393342,"uid":35737,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"𤧶？ 玩佢老母呀 <br />\n下一代用自己嘅未來<br />\n嚟同佢爭取香港人嘅自由 條友可以咁撚自私講啲咁嘅野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"唉 生意佬本身就係咁無良⋯"},{"pid":"c3a1e57e86b1da9600672d6328cbff05c7ffe57e","tid":1393342,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953a58830285de5028cff95b69a1774100783ad8","tid":1393342,"uid":233929,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"有消息指8月5號星期一，香港將有重大事情發生。<br />\n為安全起見，市民應盡量留在家中，避免工作及外出。<br />\n小心照顧小童及長者，並留意電台最新消息。"},{"pid":"f6deb3a825d5d025c14ac4ee7ee1779f00bb0a7b","tid":1393342,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例 - 政府係有誠意取消就合情合理合法地撤回整個法案<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性 - 沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者 - 沒有特首強推送終條例，何來市民上街示威，更唔會比警察拉<br />\n<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件 - 全世界都知香港黑警濫權同警黑合作的問題<br />\n<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選 - 最重要一點，一切問題起源，就係特首並非由市民選出，特首不能代表市民意願，不以民為本，只為中央考慮<br />\n<br />\n因此，五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"7a5dbae7abe00187d3e052978a91bde9861dd4b3","tid":1393342,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"31f14c69c713f3557eb66accd97e90ecfcf8063e","tid":1393342,"uid":87890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ce13273b1a59caf45d46845f4cdaf20b7f7500","tid":1393342,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897875989b02b0083846fe46b7e154b254dff24","tid":1393342,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01ae34dd724b975493a9e04ec6628a0ea355139","tid":1393342,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f14c69c713f3557eb66accd97e90ecfcf8063e","tid":1393342,"uid":87890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cc0172